        "Process_Category": "Laser Powder Bed Fusion (LPBF) + Heat Treatment",
        "Process_Text": {
          "original": "Gas-atomized powder (Al-3.89Cu-1.22Li-0.98Sc-0.43Zr wt%) fabricated using LiM-X260A LPBF machine. Process parameters: laser power 300 W, scanning velocity 1200 mm/s, hatch spacing 0.1 mm, layer thickness 40 um. Optimized heat treatment: gradual heating at 10°C/min from RT to 300°C in KSL-1400X muffle furnace, held at 300°C for 1 h, then cooled to ambient temperature in air.",
          "simplified": "LPBF of Al-Cu-Li-Sc-Zr powder using LiM-X260A machine; 300 W, 1200 mm/s, 0.1 mm hatch, 40 um layer; followed by optimized heat treatment at 300°C for 1 h with 10°C/min heating rate, air cooling."
        },
